   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"To Dorotheos, the apaitetes for tow, from Zakaon, ... geouchos. Pay to Ammonius and Apion, the epimeletes of the catholicus, what is due;  . 9 28 desmai of litras, and for 12 baskets 33 desmai, in total all 61 desmai only. I pray that you are well for a long time, my brother." (TC).</ab>
